        <p class="about-hero__tagline">— Extending Healthy Horizons —</p>
        <p class="about-hero__text">{{ section.settings.hero_text | default: "HerboVilla is the Ayurveda and herbal wellness division of PRM Pharmaceuticals — a 25-year-old Indian pharmaceutical house founded in Bhavnagar, Gujarat by Mr. Hemang Soni in 1999, today serving 35,000+ satisfied customers across 28+ states and 3 international markets through 300+ distributor channels." }}</p>
