          <div class="about-leader__body">
            <div class="about-leader__head">
              <div>
                <h3 class="about-leader__name">Mr. Hemang Soni</h3>
                <p class="about-leader__role">Founder &amp; Managing Director · PRM Pharmaceuticals</p>
                <p class="about-leader__since">Leading since 1999 · Bhavnagar, Gujarat</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="about-leader__bio">A first-generation pharmaceutical entrepreneur who founded PRM Pharmaceuticals in 1999 in Bhavnagar, Gujarat with a single conviction — that quality Indian medicine should reach every household, not just metro pharmacies. Over 25+ years, he has built PRM into one of Gujarat's leading Pharma O.T.C. houses with <strong>85+ brands</strong>, <strong>250+ formulations</strong>, a distributor network spanning <strong>28+ Indian states and 3 international markets</strong>, and a WHO-GMP facility that manufactures both allopathic and Ayurvedic portfolios to the same discipline.</p>

            <p class="about-leader__bio">In 2013, responding to a rising demand for authentic, safety-tested Ayurvedic medicines, he launched <strong>HerboVilla</strong> — the group's Ayurveda and herbal wellness division. His insistence that the Ayurvedic line use the exact same WHO-GMP production standards as the allopathic line is the reason HerboVilla exists at all.</p>

            <div class="about-leader__timeline">
              <div><span>1999</span>Founded PRM Pharmaceuticals · Launched Corylplus™</div>
              <div><span>2010</span>Commissioned WHO-GMP Bhavnagar facility</div>
              <div><span>2013</span>Launched HerboVilla — Ayurveda division</div>
              <div><span>2018</span>AYUSH licensed · 3 international markets</div>
              <div><span>2024</span>35,000+ customers · 300+ distributor channels</div>
            </div>

            <ul class="about-leader__beliefs">
              <li><strong>Ayurveda is healthcare, not folklore</strong> — every HerboVilla formulation is traceable to Ayurvedic Pharmacopoeia texts (A.B. / BHP standards).</li>
              <li><strong>Quality is non-negotiable</strong> — championed WHO-GMP, Schedule T/M and ISO 9001:2015 compliance from day one.</li>
              <li><strong>Medicine must be accessible</strong> — built pricing, pack sizes and 300+ distributor channels so rural India is served with the same product Mumbai gets.</li>
            </ul>

            <blockquote class="about-leader__quote">
              <p>"Ayurveda is the knowledge of life. Our job is to preserve that knowledge at full potency, then deliver it with the safety and discipline of modern pharma. Nothing is more sacred than getting that right."</p>
              <cite>— Mr. Hemang Soni, Founder</cite>
            </blockquote>

            <div class="about-leader__stats">
              <div><span>25+</span> Years Building PRM</div>
              <div><span>85+</span> Brands Launched</div>
              <div><span>300+</span> Distribution Partners</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="about-leader about-leader--rich about-leader--photo">
          <div class="about-leader__portrait">
            {%- if section.settings.leader_image_2 != blank -%}
