            <p class="about-leader__bio">The second-generation leader carrying PRM's quality legacy into the digital era. A <strong>B. Pharmacy</strong> graduate followed by a <strong>Masters in Finance from IIT-Delhi</strong>, Dhyey formally joined the family business in 2020 and now leads HerboVilla's modernisation — direct-to-consumer commerce, data-driven formulation research, and public education on Ayurveda as preventive healthcare.</p>

            <p class="about-leader__bio">Under his leadership, HerboVilla launched its dedicated D2C channel in 2023, expanded its in-house phytochemistry lab, and now runs one of the most transparent label-and-dosing programmes in Indian Ayurveda — classical texts on one side, standardised extracts and lab reports on the other.</p>

