              <div><span>2023</span>Launched HerboVilla D2C platform</div>
              <div><span>2024</span>Scaling Ayurveda to young India</div>
            </div>

            <ul class="about-leader__beliefs">
              <li><strong>Evidence meets tradition</strong> — pairing classical Ayurvedic texts with rigorous in-house phytochemistry and standardised extracts.</li>
              <li><strong>Ayurveda needs to speak to young India</strong> — clear labels, honest dosing, transparent sourcing, no mystic marketing.</li>
              <li><strong>Awareness is therapy</strong> — ongoing content, education and herbal literacy as a brand responsibility, not a campaign.</li>
            </ul>

            <blockquote class="about-leader__quote">
              <p>"My generation deserves Ayurveda that's been tested, not just told. We're building HerboVilla as a bridge — so a 25-year-old in Bangalore can trust what her grandmother in Bhavnagar has trusted for decades."</p>
