          <p class="process-step__text">Herbs sourced from verified organic farms and contract growers across Rajasthan, Kerala, Himachal, and Gujarat — seed-to-soil traceable.</p>
        </li>

        <li class="process-step">
          <div class="process-step__num">02</div>
          <div class="process-step__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" aria-hidden="true">
