              <path d="M12 10V6M28 10V6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="process-step__title">Safety Screening</h3>
          <p class="process-step__text">Each lot is screened for heavy metals (Pb, Hg, Cd, As), pesticide residue, aflatoxins, and microbial load in our QC lab.</p>
        </li>

        <li class="process-step">
          <div class="process-step__num">04</div>
          <div class="process-step__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" aria-hidden="true">
